<h2>What Is On-Page SEO?</h2>
<p>On-page SEO is the process of optimizing elements on your website to help Google understand your pages and rank them higher. It affects how your content, structure, and keywords perform in search results.</p>

<p>Key elements include:</p>
<ul>
<li>Content quality and optimization</li>
<li>Keyword research and placement</li>
<li>Meta tags (title, description, headings)</li>
<li>Internal linking to related pages</li>
<li>URL structure and page speed</li>
</ul>

<p>Businesses in Kenya use <a href="#services" style="color:#f39c12;font-weight:bold;">on-page SEO services</a> to improve local visibility and drive targeted traffic to their websites.</p>
</section>

